patthana16.89:4.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ rūpāvacaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho narūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.89:4.3: Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha … pe … ārammaṇe tīṇi … pe … avigate cha.
patthana16.89:5.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ narūpāvacaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho nanarūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
